{"tid":466593,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"$1200 求藍芽耳機/線推薦","createTime":"2017-11-12T16:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T02:02:59.000Z","uid":29850,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"444caa4bf12e30695e79e92c1221e9cd50563ab3","tid":466593,"uid":29850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:53:51.000Z","msg":"$1200 budget<br />\n用ip7+<br />\n本身有隻westone w10同im50 <br />\n唔太鐘意成日要插3.5mm 轉lightning頭<br />\n所以想買藍芽耳機或者線<br />\n<br />\n耳機暫時睇佐<br />\n1. Jaybird X3<br />\n2. Shure wireless se215<br />\n但個design唔係幾鐘意 同埋比較鐘意westone個種入耳式<br />\n<br />\n線既話上網睇佐幾隻品牌<br />\n1. Westone bluetooth $8XX<br />\n2. Shure bluetooth $8XX<br />\n3. Prostereo L5 $6XX<br />\n想問第三個品牌有無巴打用緊 <br />\n見佢性價比幾高 材料比大牌子好 係電量差少少<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打覺得呢個budget買藍芽耳機/定就咁買線算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e32d9fc32ba43ec685db35bfcdfe0cdd90a56dd","tid":466593,"uid":29850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:56:29.000Z","msg":"唔記得佐問 邊隻牌子無咁易聽聽下斷線"},{"pid":"19af8019535b63cc39b6ca4d3305938d94a392f8","tid":466593,"uid":86288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:03:46.000Z","msg":"Aftershokz👍🏻"},{"pid":"43f86c133b1450c2a42c634bedaab24f13e907fe","tid":466593,"uid":21197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:04:53.000Z","msg":"BeatsX"},{"pid":"244e7fdf24c932b0bc32e3b1502a33617b3fa78a","tid":466593,"uid":22946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"Westone Wx"},{"pid":"332cc70c30840a44cb3281531ed62deb0202b222","tid":466593,"uid":82970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"咩都好如果有人推215 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就一定唔好</span></span>，話咩抵買都係買個模戴個舒服，買藍芽耳機都係買返專做運動耳機既大廠，音質唔差之餘，電量同藍芽技術上都有一定水準"},{"pid":"213fd90e57ea84e3323ec78adeb8bc5f555fabad","tid":466593,"uid":29850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"